---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 574
Tags:
  - Life-Love=The Primordial State=Purity, Simplicity, Wholeness
By: Lieh-tse
---
The true reason underlying things is invisible, unseizable. indefinable,
indeterminable.  Only the spirit established in the state of perfect natural
simplicity can attain it in profound contemplation.
